FBIS3-22080 "jptdd013__l94083" JPRS-tdd-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 24 March 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Police Seize 700,000 Mandrax Tablets MB2403113294 Johannesburg SAPA in English 1056 GMT 24 Mar 94 MB2403113294 Johannesburg SAPA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Cape Town March 24 SAPA -- Narcotics detectives acting on information seized 70,000 mandrax tablets with an estimated street value of more than R[Rand]1 million in Khayelitsha in the Cape Peninsula on Wednesday. The policemen searched the canopy of a bakkie [pick-up truck] and found the tablets hidden in a secret compartment. Four men were arrested.
